#: ../../M/mickey-mouse-program.rst:9
msgid ""
"North American equivalent of a :ref:`noddy` (that is, trivial) program. "
"Doesn't necessarily have the belittling connotations of mainstream slang "
"\"Oh, that's just mickey mouse stuff! \"; sometimes trivial programs can be "
"very useful."
msgstr ""
":ref:`noddy`\\ (つまり些細な)プログラムの北米での同義語。主流のスラング「Oh, that's just mickey mouse "
"stuff!(ああ、そんなのただのミッキーマウスだ!)」の見下した含みを必ずしも持つわけではない。時には些細なプログラムが非常に役立つこともある。"
